<title>USA: Barney's investor deadline extended to August 22.</title>
<headline>Barney's investor deadline extended to August 22.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Barney's Inc and its creditors' committee said Friday they have extended the deadline for execution of a definitive agreement with Dickson Concepts (International) Ltd.</p>
<p>The deadline has been extended to August 22.</p>
<p>Barney's and the creditors' committee said they agreed to the extension with Isetan Co Ltd, its former business partner. Barney's said Dickson also agreed to the extension.</p>
<p>A court hearing on the motion to allow bid protections to Dickson is set to occur on or before August 29, the bankrupt retailer said.</p>
<p>Barney's filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy reorganization on January 10, 1996.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
